// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5305 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5568bc07-25d1-583c-9087-bd24fb957750

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
